snippet.title: Longplay of Winter Olympic Games: Lillehammer '94
snippet.description:
Longplay of Winter Olympic Games: Lillehammer '94, played as the NTSC version on the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. This game's version was released in Feb. 1994. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:13 - Intro
01:33 - Opening Ceremony
02:14 - Downhill
03:58 - Luge
06:49 - Moguls
08:44 - SuperG
10:03 - Bobsleigh
12:18 - Ski Jump
13:26 - Biathlon
15:56 - Giant Slalom
17:45 - Short Track
19:14 - Slalom
20:50 - Ending Ceremony
21:16 - Fails

By: Retro Game Spacko
